	<!-- Native Help / Reference window. Mirrors EQUI_NativeCollectionWnd.xml's
	     layout and coordinate scheme, minus the Items list, since there is no
	     per-character progress to show here, just static documentation, so
	     the Detail panel's body label simply owns the extra vertical space
	     that would otherwise go to a sub-list. Non-sizable (like the
	     original Achievements window) since nothing here needs to grow on
	     resize; no ReflowIfResized required client-side. -->

